articles.title: EU fails to agree on Russia oil embargo, to try again Monday before summit - Reuters.com
articles.description: The EU failed on Sunday to agree on an embargo of Russian oil, but diplomats but will still try to make progress ahead of a Monday-Tuesday summit on an exemption for pipeline deliveries to landlocked Central European countries, officials said.
